{"tid":956071,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"可憐棕熊吃聖誕大餐　把大媽手臂整隻咬斷吞下","createTime":"2018-12-26T03:47:47.000Z","updateTime":"2018-12-26T14:17:50.000Z","uid":130626,"like":19,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":10,"replies":[{"pid":"77d730849d7c9b24fdd06fbaaf65a06a96d8ed47","tid":956071,"uid":130626,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-12-26T03:47:47.000Z","msg":"俄羅斯一隻棕熊日前和人類一起度過聖誕節派對，但其中一名53歲大媽突然伸手進入棕熊的籠子裡，棕熊可能誤以為是聖誕大餐，竟直接把大媽的一隻手臂整隻咬掉吞下，導致大媽大量失血送醫急救，目前仍在醫院治療當中。<br />\n據英國《每日郵報》報導，事發在阿欽斯克(Achinsk)，這隻攻擊人的棕熊由當地一間旅館的老闆飼養，平時牠的工作就是娛樂顧客。不過這隻棕熊長期被飼主關在籠子裡飼養，平時若要餵牠，也都會透過夾子或棍子把食物遞進籠子。但就在前幾日，旅館老闆犒賞員工，辦了一場聖誕趴，其中一名大媽員工在酒後，向其他人吹噓自己很有辦法馴服棕熊，於是直接把手伸進籠子，結果慘遭棕熊咬掉一隻手臂並吃下。<br />\n這名大媽大量失血並被送醫急救，目前仍在醫院救治當中。警方表示，並不會對這隻棕熊處死，並預計春天能將牠野放。據悉這名旅館老闆養了兩隻棕熊，而這些棕熊非常乖，也很聰明，平時和遊客互動時，會故意張開嘴巴接蘋果吃。（施旖婕／綜合外電報導）<br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/uPvPAw6.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FuPvPAw6.png&h=5ab437d7&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/mrhVv5s.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FmrhVv5s.png&h=cad761db&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/j8mZXLt.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2Fj8mZXLt.png&h=bd2096b5&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/w9iajYO.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2Fw9iajYO.png&h=eb45ee30&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/H6js6DP.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FH6js6DP.png&h=eb4f84da&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<a href=\"https://tw.news.appledaily.com/international/realtime/20181226/1489948\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Ftw.news.appledaily.com%2Finternational%2Frealtime%2F20181226%2F1489948&d=Fnn%2Flz3z3YGUq6w1LWtuEnIou9iuErJt32EjuWI86Zw%3D&h=42384de1\" data-ef-url=\"https://embed.lih.kg/frame?u=https%3A%2F%2Ftw.news.appledaily.com%2Finternational%2Frealtime%2F20181226%2F1489948&h=c9b9002a\" target=\"_blank\">https://tw.news.appledaily.com/international/realtime/20181226/1489948</a>"},{"pid":"16587e9853f38e1ae007d36ef0aef95b42314569","tid":956071,"uid":220701,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-12-26T03:53:23.000Z","msg":"大媽<img src=\"/assets/faces/xm/wonder.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"dcadfdf3382686aa0fc192affbe571b8f996cb35","tid":956071,"uid":55533,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-12-26T03:55:28.000Z","msg":"熊<img src=\"/assets/faces/xm/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/xm/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/xm/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"2866968efb2270c38ff51e249e3fd74f04d17739","tid":956071,"uid":139700,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-12-26T03:57:12.000Z","msg":"中國人定俄羅斯人?"},{"pid":"640d735566ec806e9c4e1dc34a5f806b59ed339b","tid":956071,"uid":65030,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-12-26T03:59:05.000Z","msg":"仲野放<img src=\"/assets/faces/xm/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"2be33604597a77ab17c0d1b6bf3db1ce1e1e309c","tid":956071,"uid":130626,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"quote":{"pid":"dcadfdf3382686aa0fc192affbe571b8f996cb35","tid":956071,"uid":55533,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-12-26T03:55:28.000Z","msg":"熊<img src=\"/assets/faces/xm/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/xm/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/xm/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-12-26T13:16:48.000Z","msg":"唔洗死已經好好啦"},{"pid":"e952d3e303a6525bbb8965d737bc4ac03153a2b3","tid":956071,"uid":209773,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-12-26T13:30:56.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/xm/good.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />  俾個like for唔殺死隻熊"},{"pid":"6c5f033a1ca1830fa1a741909e1ad0bc2102ef37","tid":956071,"uid":25559,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2